name: I'm Rich, Momm.
description:
Welcome to the world of Kim Jor. A mischievous little Forpus who loves to travel around in his mother's dreamland. You will get beautiful images in a variety of styles with the purple forpus is hidden. Yes, he is Mr.Kim Jor. Enjoy in my cute dreamland. 

This Edition is rare. Let's celebrates the Chinese New Year. KimJor comes in a red Chinese dress. It represents good luck, abundance and wealth. There are also many auspicious items such as goldfish, gold, Chinese lions, firecrackers. May everyone be rich. good health this year.
